Class GameStateTask

All Implemented Interfaces:
IRealTimeTask, ITask
public class GameStateTask
extends RealTimeTask

GameStateTask extends RealTimeTask to change the current active GameState.

GameStateTask execution logic: 1. Validate the given enumeration is not the current active state. 3. Clear the BasicPassManager. 4. Clear the GUI Display. 5. Deactivate all input. 6. Initialize the new active GameState.

GameStateTask does not have a more detailed 'equals' comparison. All GameStateTask are considered 'equal', therefore, a newer version can always replace the older one.
